Jesus Christ, have mercy on us, &lt;br/&gt;
Saviour of the whole world, &lt;br/&gt;
have mercy on us and hear, &lt;br/&gt;
O Lord, our voices; &lt;br/&gt;
Lord, give to all of us&lt;br/&gt;
life and peace in our land, &lt;br/&gt;
